geo":{},"id":"1999807644840940017","in_reply_to_user_id":"1741993395910811648","lang":"zh","note_tweet":{"entities":{}},"possibly_sensitive":false,"public_metrics":{"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":2,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"reply_count":1,"retweet_count":0},"referenced_tweets":[{"id":"1999807534698537065","type":"replied_to"}],"reply_settings":"everyone","text":"（2）\n最后的想法是还好只吸了一口，然后语音记录安静下来。停滞。比以往任何体验都强烈且独特，纯粹到极致的空无。什么都没有的状态会带来不安，预设的指引起到了作用，我尝试寻找呼吸，并且集中在呼吸上，等待一切回来\n我记得幻觉是有内容的，多色的，可能没有什么含义，但我不记得图像是什么样的"}],"users":[{"created_at":"2024-01-02T01:22:57.000Z","description":"猫，诗歌，精神动力学。艺术，朝闻道，波粒二象性。不断寻找着广播塔的星际候鸟。 | “我们彻夜飞旋，直至没入火焰。” | 匿名提问箱⬇️ | 🚪88/158","entities":{"url":{"urls":[{"display_url":"ngl.link/anincandescenc…","end":23,"expanded_url":"https://ngl.link/anincandescence1","start":0,"url":"https://t.co/iO6MRJNm9j"}]}},"id":"1741993395910811648","location":"天鹅座X-1","name":"炽烈已极","pinned_tweet_id":"1991299586002935866","profile_image_url":"https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1999154150693797888/7aGBwxD0_normal.jpg","protected":false,"public_metrics":{"followers_count":1329,"following_count":219,"like_count":11709,"listed_count":4,"media_count":897,"tweet_count":4688},"url":"https://t.co/iO6MRJNm9j","username":"AnIncandescence","verified":false}]}}